<h5 id="subject_1105751">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=124198.msg1105751#msg1105751" rel="nofollow">Re: 关于高科技护甲剩下的部分</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1105751'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1105751'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
