<h5 id="subject_1105753">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=124198.msg1105753#msg1105753" rel="nofollow">Re: 关于高科技护甲剩下的部分</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1105753'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1105753'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #4 于:</strong> 2021-03-27, 周六 00:06:14 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1105753_quick_mod"></div>
